; ====================================================
; Cutscene 6 - Maria birthday
; Four decoration items spawn around Maria. Dialogue
; 0 asks the player which date it is; on the birthday
; branch Maria speaks text 184 ("glad you remembered")
; else text 201 (surprise). Reinteract shows text 200
; ("cooked something special"). Baby-hold pose variant
; triggers if HAVE_BABY is set.
; ====================================================
.cs_6:
