; Cutscene 16 - Popuri baby-name confirmation
; Parallel of .cs_9. Dialogue 30 picks midwife / potion
; dealer / Lillia. Midwife text 280 - 211; potion
; dealer text 280 - 213; Lillia text 281, 280, 282.
; ====================================================
.cs_16:
